text: Germani may refer to * Germanic peoples, a collection of northern European ethnic groups in Roman times * Germani (Oretania), pre-Roman ancient people of the Iberian Peninsula * Germani cisrhenani, a group of tribes that lived during classical times to the west of the Rhine river *Vita Germani, a hagiographic text written by Constantius of Lyon in the 5th century AD * Germani (surname)
title: Germani (disambiguation)
